			<h4><a id="comment_link_64116569" name="comment_link_64116569" href="//entertainment.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23176501&amp;cid=64116569" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64116569)" >To What End?</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64116569" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64116569); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Interesting)</span></h4>
