		<div id="comment_body_64117865"><p>They need a PAL one, not an NTSC one, and the ones in North America will all be NTSC. The 25fps of PAL was closer to the film FPS of 24, so they used a PAL D1 when they recorded the series, despite being intended for NTSC broadcast. Ya, it's somewhat strange, but it saved them a lot of time/money in rendering.</p></div>
